00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:13.500
Malai Kofta Curry - cheese balls gravy

00:02:39.341 --> 00:02:45.800
garam masal 1/2 tsp, coriander pdr - 1/2 tsp, chilli pdr 1/2 tsp, cardamom pdr - 1/4 tsp

00:02:48.766 --> 00:02:55.700
ginger garlic -paste - 1/2 tsp, cumin seed - 1/2 tsp, chopped garlic - 1 tbsp

00:02:55.700 --> 00:02:59.200
ground paste of 10 to 12 cashews

00:03:02.214 --> 00:03:05.700
chopped onion (3 no. )

00:03:10.800 --> 00:03:14.813
tomato puree from 3 tomatoes

00:03:16.400 --> 00:03:20.495
2 or 3 tbsp of fresh cream

00:03:25.948 --> 00:03:30.400
add cumin seed, garlics, curry leaves

00:03:47.744 --> 00:03:52.700
saute onions till they turn brown

00:03:55.700 --> 00:03:59.231
Add tomato puree, saute it well till the raw smell goes off, don't add salt or spices now

00:04:18.200 --> 00:04:25.700
After sauting you can add spices,salt

00:04:34.473 --> 00:04:37.900
let it boil for 5 minutes

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:50.000
cashew paste

00:04:52.900 --> 00:04:59.900
now the gravy is going to be thick because of cashew paste, so add required water

00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:14.100
finally, turn off the stove and add fresh cream ( 2 tbsp )

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:58.000
dip the koftas at the time of serving ( do not boil koftas with gravy )

